Subject: [PATCH 32/89] Rename newStories third banner file to match import
 casing.

Fixes Linux/Vite ENOENT where Git had lowercase `new` in the filename.
---
 ...ew stories 3 - 2x.jpg => New stories 3 - 2x.jpg} | Bin
 1 file changed, 0 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
 rename resources/js/assets/newStories/{new stories 3 - 2x.jpg => New stories 3 - 2x.jpg} (100%)

diff --git a/resources/js/assets/newStories/new stories 3 - 2x.jpg b/resources/js/assets/newStories/New stories 3 - 2x.jpg
similarity index 100%
rename from resources/js/assets/newStories/new stories 3 - 2x.jpg
rename to resources/js/assets/newStories/New stories 3 - 2x.jpg
